1. *Odlaze* iz grada u potrazi za boljim poslom. (They are leaving the city in search of a better job.)
2. Kada ćeš *odlaziti* na spavanje? (When will you go to bed?)
3. Oni su već *odlazili* kada smo stigli. (They had already left when we arrived.)
4. Da li si ikada *odlazio* u inostranstvo? (Have you ever traveled abroad?)
5. *Odlazi* od mene, ne mogu da te gledam. (Go away from me, I can't stand to look at you.)
6. Oni *odlaze* na godišnji odmor sledeće nedelje. (They are leaving for their vacation next week.)
7. Ne želim da *odlazim* odavde dok ne završim ovaj posao. (I don't want to leave here until I finish this job.)
8. Mama me uvek *prati* kada *odlazim* kući. (Mom always follows me when I leave home.)
9. Oni su bili spremni da *odlaze* čim se pruži prilika. (They were ready to leave as soon as the opportunity arose.)
10. *Odlazeći* na fakultet, napravio sam mnogo novih prijatelja. (By going to college, I made a lot of new friends.)